const phoneData = [ {name: "I Phone x ", price: 10000000, diskon: 20}, {name: "I Phone xr ", price: 8000000, diskon: 20}, {name: "I Phone z ", price: 7000000, diskon: 20}, {name: "I Phone y ", price: 98000000, diskon: 20}, ] function Product ({name, price, diskon = 0 }){ return (

{name}

Rp {price} ({diskon} %)

Rp {parseInt(price) - parseInt(price) * (parseInt(diskon) / 100)}

) } export default Product
